comments: Great teacher at lower level, bad teacher at a higher level, stick to the easy classes.
Excellent Instructor! P. Theory is a hard class but worth it! The tests were very hard and the papers graded equally hard.
He\'s a really great professor. He has references to pop culture which makes it easier to understand. Overall it\'s not a difficult class. I am taking more classes with him.
really boring it was hard justifying coming to class rather than staying in bed.

Awesome teacher. I took pol sci twice in high school and got low B\'s each time. Prof. Dale makes it so clear and easy and is so willing to explain if you have any questions. He drops your lowest of 3 exams and almost always lets class out early.
BORING. I would rather watch paint dry.

Lectures are interesting and humorous. Very nice guy. Class can be challenging but he grades fairly. Would definitely take a class with him again. Show up for class every day, exam questions will come directly from his notes.
GREAT PROFESSOR... So Funny. So Helpful, very enjoyable lectures for anyone. Refreshing. Have taken multiple courses with him since.

Amazing amazing professor. I hated politics before taking his class, now I find them interesting. Very funny. Good teacher. Makes it easy to learn, hardly uses book. Lets us out of class early most days. Understands that not everyone loves poli sci.
Professor Dale is awesome, very clear in his lecturing, keeps it very interesting and humorous but stays on topic... Would recommend him 100%...
Dr. Dale is awesome!! Great teacher funny but not on purpose. Don\'t need book just read notes every question on tests are in the notes. I wish he taught more classes!

Dr. Dale is the MAN! He is very funny in class. I had him in a night class. You DON\'T need to buy the book if you don\'t want to. Just study your notes. All quizes and tests are on lecture. He let us out early almost every class. He is fair and also curves his tests. His exams are questions taken directly from quizes. Take this professor!
